      • fromIntToCell

        public static Cell fromIntToCell​(int x,
                                 int y)
        Return enum constant depending on input. If it is within 8x8 board, it returns valid cell on chessboard. In case of invalid x or y, it will return null.
        Parameters:
        x - position on chessboard by X axis
        y - position on chessboard by Y axis
        Returns:
        Cell if x and y are valid, else null
